    "patch_code": "private void writeBits(DataOutput header, BitSet bits, int length) throws IOException {\n    int cache = 0;\n    int shift = 7;\n    int max = length - 1;\n    for (int index = 0; index <= max ; index++){\n        boolean bit = bits.get(index);\n        cache |= (bit ? 1 : 0) << shift;\n        shift--;\n        if(shift < 0){\n            header.write(cache);\n            shift = 7;\n            cache = 0;\n        }\n    }\n    \n    if((length & 7) != 0){\n        header.write(cache);\n    }\n}",
